room_title: Escape room "Last Hope" by WeXcape in Wichita
room_description: A terrible virus caused by an earthquake, leaking from a top-secret biochemical weapon research facility is turning all the creatures that are exposed to the virus into mutated monsters. You and your group are the last human survivors left in the city. In order to stop the incurable virus from spreading throughout the globe, the source of the virus must be destroyed.
